msgid "Guest Wi-Fi"
msgstr "Gæste-wi-fi"

msgid "Guest networks"
msgstr "Gæstenetværk"

msgid "Add new guest network..."
msgstr "Tilføj nyt gæstenetværk..."

msgid "General"
msgstr "Generelt"

msgid "Security"
msgstr "Sikkerhed"

msgid "Network & DHCP"
msgstr "Netværk & DHCP"

msgid "Firewall"
msgstr "Firewall"

msgid "Enabled"
msgstr "Aktiveret"

msgid "Network name (SSID)"
msgstr "Netværksnavn (SSID)"

msgid "Radio"
msgstr "Radio"

msgid "Interface IP address"
msgstr "Grænseflade-IP-adresse"

msgid "Netmask"
msgstr "Netmaske"

msgid "DHCP range start"
msgstr "DHCP-intervalstart"

msgid "Lowest leased address, as offset from the network address."
msgstr "Laveste leasede adresse, som offset fra netværksadressen."

msgid "DHCP client limit"
msgstr "DHCP-klientgrænse"

msgid "Maximum number of leased addresses."
msgstr "Maksimalt antal leasede adresser."

msgid "DHCP lease time"
msgstr "DHCP-leasingperiode"

msgid "E.g. \"1h\", \"30m\", \"12h\". Minimum is \"2m\"."
msgstr "F.eks. \"1h\", \"30m\", \"12h\". Minimum er \"2m\"."

msgid "Encryption"
msgstr "Kryptering"

msgid "No encryption (open network)"
msgstr "Ingen kryptering (åbent netværk)"

msgid "Password"
msgstr "Adgangskode"

msgid "Client isolation"
msgstr "Klientisolering"

msgid "Blocks communication between clients on this guest network."
msgstr "Blokerer kommunikation mellem klienter på dette gæstenetværk."

msgid "Yes"
msgstr "Ja"

msgid "No"
msgstr "Nej"

msgid "Forwarding destination zone"
msgstr "Viderestillingsmålzone"

msgid "DHCP rule ports"
msgstr "DHCP-regelporte"

msgid "UDP port range for DHCP traffic, e.g. \"67-68\"."
msgstr "UDP-portinterval til DHCP-trafik, f.eks. \"67-68\"."

msgid "DNS rule port"
msgstr "DNS-regelport"

msgid "Error saving configuration:"
msgstr "Fejl under lagring af konfiguration:"

msgid ""
"A user interface for easily creating and management isolated Wi-Fi "
"networks for guests, each with its own access point, DHCP, and firewall "
"rules."
msgstr ""
"En brugergrænseflade til nemt at oprette og administrere isolerede wi-fi-"
"netværk til gæster, hver med sit eget adgangspunkt, DHCP og firewallregler."

msgid "Enable guest network."
msgstr "Aktiver gæstenetværk."

msgid "The radio on which the guest network will work."
msgstr "Den radio, som gæstenetværket vil fungere på."

msgid "MAC address"
msgstr "MAC-adresse"

msgid ""
"Override default MAC address - the range of usable addresses might be "
"limited by the driver"
msgstr ""
"Tilsidesæt standard MAC-adresse - intervallet for anvendelige adresser kan "
"være begrænset af driveren"

msgid "randomly generated"
msgstr "tilfældigt genereret"

msgid ""
"The address %s is already in use and no free address is available in the "
"172.16.0.1 - 172.31.0.1 range."
msgstr ""
"Adressen %s er allerede i brug, og der er ingen ledig adresse tilgængelig i "
"intervallet 172.16.0.1 - 172.31.0.1."

msgid ""
"Password must be at least 8 characters long (WPA-PSK/WPA2-PSK/WPA3-SAE)."
msgstr "Adgangskoden skal være mindst 8 tegn lang (WPA-PSK/WPA2-PSK/WPA3-SAE)."

msgid "WEP Open System"
msgstr "WEP Open System"

msgid "WEP Shared Key"
msgstr "WEP Shared Key"

msgid "Mixed Mode"
msgstr "Mixed Mode"

msgid "Enhanced Open"
msgstr "Enhanced Open"

msgid ""
"WPA2-PSK is recommended for most devices. WPA3-SAE offers the strongest "
"security but requires WPA3-capable clients."
msgstr ""
"WPA2-PSK anbefales til de fleste enheder. WPA3-SAE giver den stærkeste "
"sikkerhed, men kræver WPA3-kompatible klienter."

msgid ""
"WEP key must be 5 or 13 ASCII characters, or 10 or 26 hexadecimal digits."
msgstr ""
"WEP-nøglen skal være 5 eller 13 ASCII-tegn eller 10 eller 26 heksadecimale "
"cifre."

msgid ""
"Firewall zone guest traffic is forwarded to (usually \"wan\"). Pick an "
"existing zone from the list or fill out the <em>-- custom --</em> field to enter "
"one manually."
msgstr ""
"Firewall-zone som gæstetrafik viderestilles til (normalt \"wan\"). Vælg en "
"eksisterende zone fra listen eller udfyld feltet <em>-- brugerdefineret --</em> "
"for at indtaste en manuelt."

msgid "Input"
msgstr "Input"

msgid "Traffic from guests to the router itself (e.g. LuCI, SSH)."
msgstr "Trafik fra gæster til selve routeren (f.eks. LuCI, SSH)."

msgid "Output"
msgstr "Output"

msgid ""
"Traffic from the router itself to guests. ACCEPT is recommended so router "
"services (DHCP, DNS) keep working."
msgstr ""
"Trafik fra selve routeren til gæster. ACCEPT anbefales, så routertjenester "
"(DHCP, DNS) fortsat fungerer."

msgid "Forward"
msgstr "Viderestilling"

msgid ""
"Traffic passing between guests and other networks/zones (e.g. LAN). Keep "
"this REJECT or DROP to isolate guests from your LAN. ACCEPT would allow "
"guests to reach other networks."
msgstr ""
"Trafik, der passerer mellem gæster og andre netværk/zoner (f.eks. LAN). Behold "
"dette på REJECT eller DROP for at isolere gæster fra dit LAN. ACCEPT vil "
"tillade gæster at nå andre netværk."

msgid "accept"
msgstr "accepter"

msgid "reject"
msgstr "afvis"

msgid "drop"
msgstr "drop"

msgid "driver default"
msgstr "driverstandard"